            "title": "Diurnal roosting preferences of cave-dwelling bats in Northeastern Agusan Del Norte, Mindanao, Philippines",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Dennis",
                    "lastName": "Warguez"
                },
